00:04:07.940 --> 00:04:10.660 align:middle line:84%
And in a succession
of events that

00:04:10.660 --> 00:04:13.960 align:middle line:84%
allows me to have a conscious
voice to say, hey, look,

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:17.470 align:middle line:84%
everything that you're
afraid of, pain, suffering,

00:04:17.470 --> 00:04:19.899 align:middle line:84%
losing everything,
