00:04:19.899 --> 00:04:21.459 align:middle line:90%
already been through all that.

00:04:21.459 --> 00:04:24.160 align:middle line:84%
I've been through
it so often that I

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:28.030 align:middle line:84%
chose to be at the bedside of
people going from this world

00:04:28.030 --> 00:04:31.510 align:middle line:84%
to the next, and to help
develop and create programming

00:04:31.510 --> 00:04:35.380 align:middle line:84%
that now the VA has the No
Vet Die Alone program, which

00:04:35.380 --> 00:04:37.360 align:middle line:84%
came from the Twilight
Brigade, which

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:39.940 align:middle line:90%
is what you help me build.

00:04:39.940 --> 00:04:42.910 align:middle line:84%
And now by creating
these programmings

00:04:42.910 --> 00:04:45.610 align:middle line:84%
and be able to bring
this knowledge forward,

00:04:45.610 --> 00:04:47.920 align:middle line:84%
I look at palliative
and end-of-life care

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.970 align:middle line:84%
and knowing in
this next pandemic,

00:04:49.970 --> 00:04:51.770 align:middle line:90%
