00:04:54.460 --> 00:04:57.640 align:middle line:84%
and being there,
the critical things

00:04:57.640 --> 00:05:03.200 align:middle line:84%
that people have to decide
is take a good look at death.

00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:05.150 align:middle line:84%
Because remember,
George, in life, there

00:05:05.150 --> 00:05:06.427 align:middle line:90%
are things that are certain--

00:05:06.427 --> 00:05:07.760 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: And that's one of them.

00:05:07.760 --> 00:05:09.210 align:middle line:90%
>>BRINKLEY: Certainty.

00:05:09.210 --> 00:05:11.600 align:middle line:84%
And if you breathing,
you're leaving.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.410 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yep.

00:05:12.410 --> 00:05:15.050 align:middle line:84%
>>BRINKLEY: And it's
guaranteed and inevitable,

00:05:15.050 --> 00:05:18.470 align:middle line:84%
and I've taken that
on myself to do.

00:05:18.470 --> 00:05:20.720 align:middle line:84%
I've always talked about
that the battle for the souls

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:22.762 align:middle line:84%
of humankind would be
fought in the health care--

00:05:22.762 --> 00:05:25.520 align:middle line:84%
you've been listening
to that for 18 years--

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:28.760 align:middle line:84%
and that we are there
and that this program

00:05:28.760 --> 00:05:31.070 align:middle line:84%
would come into play, which
is what we're watching now,

00:05:31.070 --> 00:05:34.850 align:middle line:84%
called the lockdown or the
pandemic, would come into play.

00:05:34.850 --> 00:05:38.450 align:middle line:84%
And that when you think about
the battle for the souls

00:05:38.450 --> 00:05:41.560 align:middle line:84%
of humankind being
fought in health care,

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:43.690 align:middle line:84%
and you look at everything
that's distracting us,

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:46.420 align:middle line:84%
but it gets back down to health
care, then I'm pretty sure

00:05:46.420 --> 00:05:47.410 align:middle line:90%
we're there.

00:05:47.410 --> 00:05:52.530 align:middle line:84%
The thing that troubles me
is I have seen and watched

00:05:52.530 --> 00:05:56.100 align:middle line:90%
