bunches of times,

00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:01.710 align:middle line:84%
both being a hospice
volunteer for 43 years

00:06:01.710 --> 00:06:04.980 align:middle line:84%
and being with 2,013 people
going from this world

00:06:04.980 --> 00:06:05.888 align:middle line:90%
to the next.

00:06:05.888 --> 00:06:07.680 align:middle line:84%
