a conscious look at it

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.790 align:middle line:10%
and we keep driven
to be afraid, then we

00:06:14.790 --> 00:06:18.070 align:middle line:10%
lose a certain connection
to our spiritual selves.

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:21.600 align:middle line:84%
And I think that that's got
to be an important issue.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:25.920 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: MatÃ­as De Stefano
talked about his remembrances

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:29.688 align:middle line:90%
of past lives, much like you.

00:06:29.688 --> 00:06:32.230 align:middle line:84%
>>MATÃAS DE STEFANO: Unity is
not something that we are going

00:06:32.230 --> 00:06:37.690 align:middle line:84%
to live as a real
thing in this planet.

00:06:37.690 --> 00:06:41.260 align:middle line:84%
