00:06:45.490 --> 00:06:47.650 align:middle line:84%
There is no split
in times, there's

00:06:47.650 --> 00:06:51.500 align:middle line:84%
no split in perspectives,
there's no split in space.

00:06:51.500 --> 00:06:56.680 align:middle line:84%
So that's why unity is
the only state where

00:06:56.680 --> 00:07:00.670 align:middle line:84%
you could feel everything,
where you could see everything,

00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:04.160 align:middle line:90%
where you could be anywhere.

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:08.120 align:middle line:84%
Sirius for us was the
spot where we could

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:11.450 align:middle line:90%
learn how to go back to unity.

00:07:11.450 --> 00:07:15.440 align:middle line:90%
We used to call Sirius, In-Na.

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:18.950 align:middle line:10%
That's the name we had
for the two stars--

00:07:18.950 --> 00:07:23.090 align:middle line:10%
the bigger one, In,
and the small one, Na.

00:07:23.090 --> 00:07:24.030 align:middle line:10%
In-Na.

00:07:24.030 --> 00:07:26.540 align:middle line:10%
We were called the In-Na people.

00:07:26.540 --> 00:07:29.150 align:middle line:84%
And the In-Na people
has this story.

00:07:29.150 --> 00:07:32.150 align:middle line:84%
At the first beginning,
there was nothing.

00:07:32.150 --> 00:07:33.680 align:middle line:90%
There was a void.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:40.340 align:middle line:84%
And from that void, there was
a breath, a breathing that

00:07:40.340 --> 00:07:43.850 align:middle line:90%
starts to create every reality.

00:07:43.850 --> 00:07:48.860 align:middle line:84%
By that breathing, a door
was opened in the universe,

00:07:48.860 --> 00:07:50.360 align:middle line:90%
the door of the self.

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:54.830 align:middle line:84%
And the self went through
every time and every space.

00:07:54.830 --> 00:07:59.480 align:middle line:84%
We call that the M, the
portal, the H, the time,

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:01.140 align:middle line:90%
and the S, the space.

00:08:01.140 --> 00:08:06.290 align:middle line:84%
So the name for the
universe for us was Mahas.

00:08:06.290 --> 00:08:11.690 align:middle line:84%
Mahas was the creation,
was the consciousness going

00:08:11.690 --> 00:08:15.410 align:middle line:84%
from this unity
towards everything,

00:08:15.410 --> 00:08:17.390 align:middle line:90%
towards every dimension.

00:08:17.390 --> 00:08:22.490 align:middle line:84%
And after that, we realized
that, where does it go

00:08:22.490 --> 00:08:25.710 align:middle line:90%
and what is the limit of that?

00:08:25.710 --> 00:08:28.350 align:middle line:84%
But we realized that
it was limitless.

00:08:28.350 --> 00:08:29.420 align:middle line:90%
There was no end.

00:08:29.420 --> 00:08:31.080 align:middle line:90%
There was no purpose.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:33.799 align:middle line:84%
So the only purpose
that we had was

00:08:33.799 --> 00:08:37.460 align:middle line:84%
to try to understand
every space, to understand

00:08:37.460 --> 00:08:41.990 align:middle line:84%
every time, and then bring them
all to the portal to the self

00:08:41.990 --> 00:08:42.943 align:middle line:90%
again.

00:08:42.943 --> 00:08:45.110 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Dannion, do all
